textDelta: What percentage of GDP is spent on the military by Saudi Arabia since 2017? This statistic shows the percentage of GDP spent on the military by Saudi Arabia since 2017. In 2017, Saudi Arabia spent 3.2 percent of its GDP on the military.

ops.insert: During what war did Francis Scott Key write the words to 'The Star-Spangled Banner'?

textDelta: During what war did Francis Scott Key write the words to 'The Star-Spangled Banner'? Francis Scott Key wrote the words to 'The Star-Spangled Banner' during the War of 1812. Key was aboard a British ship in Baltimore Harbor on Sept. 13, 1814, when he saw the American flag still flying over Fort McHenry. The fort had withstood a British bombardment the night before. The sight inspired Key to write the poem. What is the name of the national anthem of the United States? The national anthem of the United States
